{{en-noun|catachreses}}

# A [[misuse]] of a [[word]]; an [[application]] of a [[term]] to something which it does not properly [[denote]].<ref name="OED"/>
# {{lb|en|rhetoric}} A [[misapplication]] or [[overextension]] of [[figurative]] or [[analogical]] [[description]]; a [[wrong]]ly-applied [[metaphor]] or [[trope]].<ref name="OED"/>

